name: Kembang Kantil
description:
for women of dusk, bloody soil, 
ripped heart, torn clothes,
empty street, abandoned bridge, 
failed birth, house ruin,
fractured trees, uneasy night


[Kembang Kantil is a flower that has been associated with magic and a famous female ghost called Kuntilanak, a ghost whose death was caused by childbirth. However in some other tales, she was actually the victim of rape and in some areas it's believed that Kuntilanak mainly prey on men. This art comes from a chatter in our house that if Kuntilanak is really exist, she must be our ally.] 


- 4000x6000
- 300 DPI
- Digital painting
